                "kind": "range",
                "text": "\nEMOTIONAL AND PSYCHOLOGICAL BENEFITS \nAdded meaning to life -Having a social impact and connecting with others is one of the best things for one's mental health. Citizens Advice Bureau published a study that also found that volunteering boosts ",
